ZH: 我收到一张便条，请明天去见老板。
EN: I received a note to meet the boss tomorrow.

ZH: 他给我留了一张便条，告诉我会迟到。
EN: He left me a note saying he will be late.

ZH: 她在便条上写道，感谢我的帮助。
EN: She wrote in the note, thanking me for my help.

ZH: 请在便条上写明你的联系方式。
EN: Please write your contact information on the note.

ZH: 这是我昨天留给你的便条，请查看一下。
EN: This is the note I left for you yesterday, please take a look.

ZH: 他用便条提醒我开会的时间。
EN: He used a note to remind me of the meeting time.

ZH: 你可以通过便条告诉我你的需求。
EN: You can inform me of your needs through a note.

ZH: 请在便条上写明需求和意见。
EN: Please write your needs and opinions on the note.

ZH: 我通过便条告诉了他我们的计划。
EN: I informed him of our plan through a note.

ZH: 如果你不在，我会给你留一张便条。
EN: If you're not here, I will leave a note for you.

ZH: 他经常用便条与同事交流信息。
EN: He often communicates with his colleagues through notes.

ZH: 请在便条上写清楚要求。
EN: Please write your requests clearly on the note.

ZH: 我要给老师留一张便条请假。
EN: I need to leave a note for the teacher to request leave.

ZH: 请关掉电灯，上面有便条提醒。
EN: Please turn off the light, there's a reminder note on it.

ZH: 他在便条上写下了他的抱怨。
EN: He wrote his complaints on the note.

ZH: 老板给我一张便条，说明了下一步要做的事情。
EN: The boss gave me a note, outlining the next steps to take.

ZH: 张先生总是给同事们写便条鼓励他们。
EN: Mr. Zhang always writes notes to encourage his colleagues.

ZH: 他忘记了今天的会议，直到他看到便条才想起来。
EN: He forgot about today's meeting until he saw the note.

ZH: 请通过便条向我反馈你的建议。
EN: Please provide your feedback on your suggestions through a note.

ZH: 我在门口发现了一张便条，是送货员留的。
EN: I found a note at the door, left by the delivery man.
